://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1650127623", "stars": 1667, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 21, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 383800, "username": "hideonwhere", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hideonwhere", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9038/6bba/383800_mini.png?m=1551944219", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9038/6bba/383800_normal.png?m=1551944219", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9038/6bba/383800_large.png?m=1551944219", "created": 1550124350, "last_modified": 1551944219}, "last_reply_by": "ns20", "last_touched": 1652501120, "title": "现在一周上 5 天的公司多吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/852650", "created": 1652427956, "deleted": 0, "content": "去年年中找的工作，面的大部分都是大小周 之前几年都是双休 第一次遇上大小周\r\n上了一年了，周六上班配上特色调休真的心力交瘁", "content_rendered": "去年年中找的工作，面的大部分都是大小周 之前几年都是双休 第一次遇上大小周<br />上了一年了，周六上班配上特色调休真的心力交瘁", "last_modified": 1652427956, "replies": 52, "id": 852650}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 184687, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3475, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 459546, "username": "zhaotian5868", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhaotian5868", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b58c830c9d8638f289762998fb4a5934?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b58c830c9d8638f289762998fb4a5934?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b58c830c9d8638f289762998fb4a5934?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1576487102, "last_modified": 1576487102}, "last_reply_by": "vvv7000", "last_touched": 1652436953, "title": "持续收藏很多年的特殊视频资源的存储方案有推荐吗？要兼顾私密安全和成本。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/852632", "created": 1652422762, "deleted": 0, "content": "目前是存放于一个机械移动硬盘上，为了私密没有做多余备份。一旦丢失或者坏掉就功亏一篑了。", "content_rendered": "<p>目前是存放于一个机械移动硬盘上，为了私密没有做多余备份。一旦丢失或者坏掉就功亏一篑了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1652422762, "replies": 48, "id": 852632}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_large.png?m=1651565926", "name": "linux", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1651565926", "title": "Linux", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux", "topics": 6691, "footer": "", "header": "Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.", "title_alternative": "Linux", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1651565926", "stars": 5793, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 11, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 413388, "username": "0o0O0o0O0o", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/0o0O0o0O0o", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3c8d28727aa2095657894289acfc9083?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3c8d28727aa2095657894289acfc9083?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3c8d28727aa2095657894289acfc9083?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1558157676, "last_modified": 1651458586}, "last_reply_by": "crayygy", "last_touched": 1652504315, "title": "完全使用 Linux 桌面一年了，依然是个 Linux 新手", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/852740", "created": 1652487403, "deleted": 0, "content": "不熟悉系统目录结构，不了解 GRUB ，不了解文件系统，以及很多常识。\r\n\r\n现在问我 systemd 启动顺序、iptables table 和 chain 的执行顺序、snap flatpak appimage 的区别等等，我不去 Google 也答不上来。\r\n\r\n虽然天天用命令行，但也没有特别熟悉的命令，很依赖 bash 的自动补全。不是天天用的命令全部靠搜，要么搜自己的笔记，要么 Google 搜。\r\n\r\n没有硬核的排错能力，不敢过多个性化，不敢升级内核，只敢跟着官方滚。\r\n\r\n曾以为常用 Linux 是学习 Linux 的捷径，但这样下去我觉得再过几年也还是这个水平，各位有什么提升的心得和建议吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>不熟悉系统目录结构，不了解 GRUB ，不了解文件系统，以及很多常识。</p>\n<p>现在问我 systemd 启动顺序、iptables table 和 chain 的执行顺序、snap flatpak appimage 的区别等等，我不去 Google 也答不上来。</p>\n<p>虽然天天用命令行，但也没有特别熟悉的命令，很依赖 bash 的自动补全。不是天天用的命令全部靠搜，要么搜自己的笔记，要么 Google 搜。</p>\n<p>没有硬核的排错能力，不敢过多个性化，不敢升级内核，只敢跟着官方滚。</p>\n<p>曾以为常用 Linux 是学习 Linux 的捷径，但这样下去我觉得再过几年也还是这个水平，各位有什么提升的心得和建议吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1652487403, "replies": 40, "id": 852740}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1650095309", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1650095309", "title": "分享创造", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/create", "topics": 17756, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1650095309", "stars": 4340, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 38022, "username": "dzhou121", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dzhou121", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/48d4b45943aef2c8458b00d25dbf8edb?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/48d4b45943aef2c8458b00d25dbf8edb?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/48d4b45943aef2c8458b00d25dbf8edb?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1366739686, "last_modified": 1399874093}, "last_reply_by": "xieren58", "last_touched": 1652504424, "title": "Lapce 发布 v0.1.0 用 Rust 编写 GPU 渲染的开源代码编辑器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/852668", "created": 1652431798, "deleted": 0, "content": "https://lapce.dev\r\n\r\nLapce 主要目标是媲美 Sublime Text 的速度，以及强大的功能。\r\n\r\n新版本把 GPU 后端从 Wgpu 换到了 OpenGL ，另外就是基本功能的完善。欢迎下载试用。\r\n\r\n总体是基于 Rust 的技术栈，没有使用 web 那一套东西，所以能够保证获得最接近底层的速度。用了现在比较流行的 TreeSitter ，LSP 那一套来提供语言方面的功能。", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://lapce.dev\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://lapce.dev</a></p>\n<p>Lapce 主要目标是媲美 Sublime Text 的速度，以及强大的功能。</p>\n<p>新版本把 GPU 后端从 Wgpu 换到了 OpenGL ，另外就是基本功能的完善。欢迎下载试用。</p>\n<p>总体是基于 Rust 的技术栈，没有使用 web 那一套东西，所以能够保证获得最接近底层的速度。用了现在比较流行的 TreeSitter ，LSP 那一套来提供语言方面的功能。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1652431798, "replies": 39, "id": 852668}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1652462106", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1652462106", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 13064, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1652462106", "stars": 2349, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"id": 368919, "username": "S2Line", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/S2Line", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4731fecaeb1fcb29d79de250e444a0f9?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4731fecaeb1fcb29d79de250e444a0f9?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4731fecaeb1fcb29d79de250e444a0f9?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1544198544, "last_modified": 1544198544}, "last_reply_by": "ndxxx", "last_touched": 1652435130, "title": "润 || 留", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/852638", "created": 1652424928, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近拿了某互联网大厂 offer ，还没想清楚是否去，麻烦大家给点建议，我参考下。谢谢\r\n在目前基础上总包涨差不多 50%\r\n\r\n本五，目前还没到 27 ，北京某国企后台开发。今年准备买房，有一定房贷压力(不过目前的收入也能 cover)。\r\n\r\n润过去：\r\n优：\r\n1 、收入能有较为可观的增长，但是算了其实税后也就多不到 20 个。后期收入增长较现状应该能有较大的提高\r\n2 、以后工作选择面会更宽一些，有互联网大厂背书\r\n劣：\r\n1 、不稳定，裁员风险比较大，最近在脉脉看到马上就要有一波裁员\r\n2 、工作强度大，有被 pua 风险\r\n3 、以后估计还是会换赛道，可能外企 /国企\r\n\r\n留下来：\r\n优：\r\n1 、毕业就一直在本单位，比较稳定。单位也很稳定，不裁员，应该可以干到退休。\r\n2 、做的也是比较核心的东西，现在做架构改造，较多机会。\r\n劣：\r\n1 、目前工作强度较大，不过比互联网还是好一些，忙的时候估计一周加 3 、4 天班到 8 点半，不忙的时候不加班。\r\n2 、收入比互联网低，后期收入增长幅度比互联网差\r\n\r\n其实去年底也拿了开水团的 offer ，当时有一些考虑没去。", "content_rendered": "最近拿了某互联网大厂 offer ，还没想清楚是否去，麻烦大家给点建议，我参考下。谢谢<br />在目前基础上总包涨差不多 50%<br /><br />本五，目前还没到 27 ，北京某国企后台开发。今年准备买房，有一定房贷压力(不过目前的收入也能 cover)。<br /><br />润过去：<br />优：<br />1 、收入能有较为可观的增长，但是算了其实税后也就多不到 20 个。后期收入增长较现状应该能有较大的提高<br />2 、以后工作选择面会更宽一些，有互联网大厂背书<br />劣：<br />1 、不稳定，裁员风险比较大，最近在脉脉看到马上就要有一波裁员<br />2 、工作强度大，有被 pua 风险<br />3 、以后估计还是会换赛道，可能外企 /国企<br /><br />留下来：<br />优：<br />1 、毕业就一直在本单位，比较稳定。单位也很稳定，不裁员，应该可以干到退休。<br />2 、做的也是比较核心的东西，现在做架构改造，较多机会。<br />劣：<br />1 、目前工作强度较大，不过比互联网还是好一些，忙的时候估计一周加 3 、4 天班到 8 点半，不忙的时候不加班。<br />2 、收入比互联网低，后期收入增长幅度比互联网差<br /><br />其实去年底也拿了开水团的 offer ，当时有一些考虑没去。", "last_modified": 1652427295, "replies": 38, "id": 852638}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 18335, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2151, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 50693, "username": "Kristd", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Kristd", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ef8b68cb460650c22cd0850171a6436f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ef8b68cb460650c22cd0850171a6436f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn